revision.text: ==English== ===Contraction=== {{en-cont}} # {{eye dialect of|en|[[yeah]], [[but]]}} ===Noun=== {{en-noun}} # {{lb|en|slang|derogatory}} A [[fatuous]] [[objection]] of the kind that might begin "yeah, but..." #* '''1999''', "Pete", ''Sex shops was Re: nothing important'' (on newsgroup ''alt.support.childfree'') #*: You missed Beth's introductory '''yabbuts'''...thus condemning herself to my permanent list...once a breeder and all that... #* '''2000''', "von", ''Trust & Jealousy: A Clarification of the Situation!'' (on newsgroup ''alt.abuse.recovery'') #*: Not '''yabbuts''', but rather, "No wait, that's not how it is between us." [[Category:English non-constituents]]
